precis:
Amendments to the CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD REGULATIONS which fix the initial
"sums certain" to be paid by the Board for the BASE GRADES of wheat, amber
durum wheat, barley and designated barley delivered in the 1995-96 crop
year, effective August 1, 1995.
